{"tid":2231341,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】張沛樂收起性感迎接29歲生日　獲網友激讚：好True好Pure","createTime":"2020-10-05T14:46:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T03:00:19.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"01d51ebf040aa6358ccadf345ac1cb468834abd5","tid":2231341,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"本月7日便是張沛樂（沙律）的29歲生日，過往每年生日都很多人相約沙律吃飯，整個「生日月」的飯局每餐都豐富，也很容易令沙律變胖，所以在IG發相發文表示：「看來這個生日月過得不簡單，今晚先來一個健康自助餐吧！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然沙律這想新相收起性感，但反而獲網友大讚，因為照片中的沙律化了一個淡妝，再束起頭髮變成半馬尾，相當清純，令大家有種「好True好Pure」的感覺。"},{"pid":"141e81df67a5c8a0e92f5de445f42cd35cc7f0f3","tid":2231341,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201004/389468862212608000.jpeg/iLhIwCj5CLh5PCgEHDxO6Cr0ERyghCLLxaLit8Wi4rc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201004%2F389468862212608000.jpeg%2FiLhIwCj5CLh5PCgEHDxO6Cr0ERyghCLLxaLit8Wi4rc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ea9bd991&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47210336daa6899e666880872614b1305e24e3ce","tid":2231341,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T14:46:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200821/373590893602672640.jpeg/sbf3eI-j5I_D36tgS5N5lHND4OIzKXv5-1N3b_tTd28?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200821%2F373590893602672640.jpeg%2Fsbf3eI-j5I_D36tgS5N5lHND4OIzKXv5-1N3b_tTd28%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1cf33e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200821/373590895343308800.jpeg/Gio7CrjL8rkXvWRffhDCLNQP6N5sn5x5vtEPUb7RD1E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200821%2F373590895343308800.jpeg%2FGio7CrjL8rkXvWRffhDCLNQP6N5sn5x5vtEPUb7RD1E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2f3deec2&s={SI